{"title":"熄灭与燃烧","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":1,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"熄灭与燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都已经熄灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有风吹来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有枯蓬和黄沙卷来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说打在你脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左边是沉寂，右边是哑然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都已经熄灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭或笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恩仇、欲念、欺诈和争战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从卜辞到枯叶般的村落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论法老、僧侣、工匠或奴仆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛，都已阖上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亡灵书的最后一笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经写完，墓门关闭了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都已经熄灭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的灰烬埋在时间深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血已流干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬垂飞泻的尼罗河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经平伏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只一片废墟委弃山水间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如黑夜，如逝水，如陨落的星斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却有太阳燃烧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪明的文字和思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着苏醒的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在梦的高处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有太阳燃烧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿油油的椰枣树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔叶的棕榈和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立的大城，照耀着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清真寺绿色的圆顶以及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围绕塔尖旋舞的鸽群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有太阳燃烧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红海的海藻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咆哮不息的铁青的地中海的浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿高速公路和苏伊士运河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个民族已经昂起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉思的额头，双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举起尊严和自由"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一支支清秀的茉莉的妇女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面纱已经揭开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一双双，一双双，一双双"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪亮的大眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从长长的睫毛下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正瞩望着一个新世纪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明的降临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九四年十二月于开罗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}